Package com.montevar.monte

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RegressionModel
    Makes Linear Regression models (OLSMultipleLinearRegression) and uses the models to get the weights for prediction calculations.
    RelationshipGenerator
    Creates the covariance and correlation statistics and saves them in a RelationshipStats object (RelationshipStats).
    RelationshipStats
    Holds covariance and correlation data.
    TrialGenerator
    Runs the actual Monte Carlo simulation to predict the returns of random samples.
    TrialReturnFunction
    Uses MultivariateNormalDistribution to predict the return of a trial based on a single random number seed, feature means, and feature covariances.
